<DefaultPageLayout
    title="Late Pets"
    description="osing a pet is losing a family member. Learn how to cope with the grief and honor their memory. Petapetual offers a beautiful online pet memorial to celebrate their life."
>
    <Image
        src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1450778869180-41d0601e046e?ixlib=rb-4.1.0&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D&auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=2186"
        alt="Pets are part of the family. Honor them with a Petapetual online memorial and cherish their life with you!"
        class="w-full h-48 lg:h-64 object-cover self-center rounded"
        width="256"
        height="256"
    />

    <h1 class="text-2xl font-semibold">
        <Petapetual /> for pets across the rainbow bridge
    </h1>

    <p>
        Losing a pet is a heartbreaking experience. For many of us, our pets are
        cherished family members. They are a constant, loving presence in our
        daily lives, offering silent comfort and unconditional love. The quiet
        house, the empty spot where they used to sleep, the un-greeted return
        home... it all leaves a profound ache.
    </p>

    <p>
        This grief is real and it is deep. Because the bond we share with them
        is so special, we feel a powerful need to honor their memory when
        they're gone. We want to celebrate the joy, laughter, and comfort they
        brought into our lives. We find ourselves looking through old photos,
        remembering their funny quirks, and wanting a way to pay respects to the
        little soul who gave so much.
    </p>

    <p>
        This desire to remember is a testament to the love we shared. It’s a way
        to acknowledge their important place in our family and to have a space
        where we can reflect on that happy companionship.
    </p>

    <p>
        At <Petapetual />, we understand that this loss is the loss of family.
        We created our online memorials to offer a beautiful, lasting space
        where you can build a heartfelt tribute to your beloved companion. It’s
        a place to share your favorite photos, write down those sweet or funny
        stories, and create a permanent celebration of the life you shared. It
        gives you a special place to visit, remember, and honor the
        unconditional love they gave.
    </p>
</DefaultPageLayout>
